Record in One-run Games

2018/06/15

So far this season the Seattle Mariners have won a historically high numeber of one-run games. As of this writing they are 21 - 9, and 1/2 game up on the Astros depsite having a run-differntial of about 100 runs less. This post looks at records in onr-run games obver the years.

Libraries

library(RPostgres)
library(DBI)
library(dplyr)
